des:
This skill provides information on harvest park, which includes facts about harvest park. It also provides information such as events, clubs, school calendar, start and end date, breaks and online registration.
Here are the things you can ask Alexa about harvest park.

PLEASE NOTE THAT YOU HAVE TO PUT/SAY "ask harvest park" BEFORE THE SAMPLES PROVIDED.
example: Alexa, ask harvest park ______ 

First day of school:

which day does school start 
when does school start this year 
harvest park first day of school
when is the first day of school 
first day of school 
what is the first day of school
